Package: officedown
Type: Package
Title: 'R Markdown' Format for 'Microsoft Word' and 'Microsoft PowerPoint' Documents
Version: 0.0.6.008
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Gohel", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "david.gohel@ardata.fr"),
    person("Noam", "Ross", role = c("aut"), email = 'noam.ross@gmail.com', 
    comment = "rvg for rmarkdown implementation"))
Description: Functions for converting from 'R Markdown' documents to 'Microsoft Word' documents
 or 'Microsoft PowerPoint' presentations. It brings compatibility with functions of 
 package `officer` for the production of runs and blocks of content; ability to use table 
 styles; ability to use list styles; replacement of captions by
 captions containing a Word bookmark that can be used for cross-referencing; 
 replacement of cross-references by cross-references using fields calculated
 by Word. The syntax conforms to the bookdown cross-reference definition.
